<paragraph id="IFRS16_B55" base="F45930818"><paranum>B55</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 16"/><data name="paranum" value="B55"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0592">When a <xref base="F45929685" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0363">lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0214"/></ph></xref> includes both land and buildings elements, a <xref base="F45929747" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0382">lessor<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0222"/></ph></xref> shall assess the classification of each element as a <xref base="SL45930039" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0354">finance lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0122"/></ph></xref> or an <xref base="F45929764" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0384">operating lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0269"/></ph></xref> separately applying <xref id="IFRS16_X0463" base="F47961325" href="IFRS16_62.dita#IFRS16_62">paragraphs 62&#x2013;66</xref> and <xref id="IFRS16_X0464" base="F47961326" href="IFRS16_gB53-B58.dita#IFRS16_gB53-B58/IFRS16_gB53-B58_TI">B53&#x2013;B54</xref>. In determining whether the land element is an operating lease or a finance lease, an important consideration is that land normally has an indefinite <xref base="F45929638" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0350">economic life<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0094"/></ph></xref>.</p></body></paragraph>